Invocation Name: chef meta
des: The skill gives you all of the information you need about ChefMeta's one and only saucy seven meta spice bag. Guaranteed to change how you taste food from now on. You can ask Chef Meta anything about the spice bag. Some of the questions you can ask are: How much is it, How many people does it feed? Is it spicy? What can I use it on? Get all of your questions answered, so you can order today.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
